==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Surmounted
<hw>Sur*mount"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Arch.)</fld>
<def>Having its vertical height greater than the half span; -- said of
an arch.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Her.)</fld> <def>Partly covered by another charge;
-- said of an ordinary or other bearing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Surmounter</ent>⟦br⟧
